{"tid":1467910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公關基本術，要一單嘢無人講最好係搵更爆嘅搶輿論","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:57:45.000Z","uid":3560,"like":98,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"8baf738251605680721b3ab21e3d0be6d156759e","tid":1467910,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"而今晚係有一粒文宣核彈<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警察，機場，左輪手槍</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VQEAGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VQEAGc.png&h=8ced082e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越解釋鬼單嘢只會令大家更眾焦<br />\n無論係spin去黑警派鬼又好，spin去荃灣恐襲都好<br />\n我哋今晚係衝動咗，不割蓆，但都唔好再討論<br />\n今晚文宣同facebook只需要瘋傳<strong>警察，機場，出槍</strong>!!!!<br />\n有畫面有輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬愚民無時間智慧消化前因後果鬼定唔鬼<br />\n總之，佢哋覺得打人係唔啱，但<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國際機場出手槍更唔啱!!!</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n今晚，文宣同我煲大佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察，機場，左輪手槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">借一借巴打cap嘅圖</span>"},{"pid":"040400e5b89121df074f244fac4c415ac4259c8a","tid":1467910,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"警察，機場，出真槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bca9977cae46de99fe94c705830def7c3ae0491","tid":1467910,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"警察，機場，出真槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67b3c3bba67b9e7061ff860d5328994eb4cef08","tid":1467910,"uid":3560,"lik