!</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n今晚，文宣同我煲大佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察，機場，左輪手槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">借一借巴打cap嘅圖</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#我係禮貌撚<br />\n#我係道歉撚 #代香港政府道歉</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[幫推]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;對唔住呀，我地個政府好撚衰，我代佢道歉&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對政府不合作 唔係對市民不合作<br />\n</span></strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球道歉運動! <br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nSay 句 Sorry, 好易啫 ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#團結! Be water! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!<br />\n#816轉美元!<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！</span>"},{"pid":"4e86fd85e1af4f71f179c460b5b29939194f0450","tid":1467910,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa1a92c5e946401e665da0b